platformAttributes.ios.editorialNotes.ta.k: Capture the soul of a portrait

platformAttributes.ios.editorialNotes.st.k: This incredible filtering tool will have you looking old-timey in no time. Hipstamatics awesome app is truly like nothing weve ever seen, transforming portraits into photographs that look hundreds of years old. Plus, thanks to a Photos app extension, you can edit pics right from your library.
